---
title: Smoky Pork Chops and Guacamole with Spiced Sweet Potato Rounds
description: In this smoky dish, Mexican-spiced pork chops are topped with refreshing guacamole for a perfectly savoury combination. A satisfying side of sweet potato rounds with spiced mayo hits the spot.
